===Etymology===
[[解]] (かい, kai), ''solution'' + [[決]] (けつ, ketsu), ''decisive''

===Noun===
[[Category:Japanese nouns|かいけつ]]
'''解決''' ([[かいけつ]], [[kaiketsu]])

# a [[conclusion]] to a problem

===Verb===
[[Category:Japanese Type 3 Verbs|かいけつ]]
